1. *Opasno* je voziti bez dozvole. (It is dangerous to drive without a license.)
2. Ona je u opasnoj situaciji. (She is in a dangerous situation.)
3. Vrlo je *opasno* u ovoj ulici. (It is very dangerous in this street.)
4. Oni su u *opasnosti*. (They are in danger.)
5. *Opasno* mi je bilo. (It was dangerous for me.)